	<h2>Changes to this Policy</h2>
	<p>We reserve the right to revise this policy in the future, and the most current version of the policy will govern the use of your information. Typically, this would be because of changes to the online services in use. If any changes are made, you will be notified via a blog post, or the mailing list if you are a subscriber.</p>

	<p>If you have any questions or concerns, send an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@steamcharts.com">privacy@steamcharts.com</a>.</p>
